    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game &quot;<i>Scary pictures: Yavez - seven deadly sins</i>&quot; - will plunge you into the atmosphere of the classic and gloomy history of the Soviet times.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230790/extras/2e39baa7b6173110ac8ce722d0b0640f.avif?t=1769420510\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The happy parents of the protagonist, who have just fulfilled their dream, are not even aware of what their children faced after moving to a new home. The protagonist of the story will face many horrors and his childhood fears face to face. Laughter and joy will be replaced by creepy and nauseating feelings. The blue sky and the warm sun will turn into corridors and catacombs of an old, half-decayed building. Whether the main character will be saved and whether he will save his sister depends only on you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230790/extras/96aa45114d216e4de14fe934a8cc00fd.avif?t=1769420510\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Many choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Eight game endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Interesting story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Nostalgia</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Author's soundtracks from the developer</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230790/extras/5fdb9efdaba74f2f85a51447a4381f61.avif?t=1769420510\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the game &quot;<i>Scary pictures: Yavez - seven deadly sins</i>&quot; and enjoy the game. :)<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230790/extras/7b3c1d250a1995744ef299f31543ae5d.avif?t=1769420510\" width=616 height=308 /></span></h2>",
